           <span class="field-content">
           </span>
          </div>
          <div class="views-field views-field-nothing">
           <span class="field-content">
            <div class="media">
             <div class="pull-left">
              <img alt="[title_1]" src="https://philosophy.uncc.edu/sites/philosophy.uncc.edu/files/styles/news_image/public/fields/news/field_news_landscape_image/philosopher-statue_0_0_0.png?itok=ozT7sQ1J"/>
             </div>
             <div class="media-body">
              <h3>
               Philosophy Department Newsletter, Winter 2018
              </h3>
              <i aria-hidden="true" class="fa fa-calendar">
              </i>
              <span class="date-display-single">
               February 1, 2019
              </span>
              <br/>
              <p>
               Click
               <a href="/sites/philosophy.uncc.edu/files/media/UNCCPhilosophyNewsletter-Winter2018.pdf">
                here
               </a>
               to read the latest edition of the Philosophy department newsletter.
              </p>
              <p>
               <a alt=" Philosophy Department Newsletter, Winter 2018" class="button button-green" href="/philosophy-department-newsletter-winter-2018" title=" Philosophy Department Newsletter, Winter 2018">
                Read More
               </a>
              </p>
             </div>
            </div>
            <div class="clear_float">
            </div>
            <br/>
            <hr/>
           </span>
          </div>
         </div>
         <div class="views-row views-row-2 views-row-even">
          <div class="views-field views-field-edit-node">
           <span class="field-content">
           </span>
          </div>
          <div class="views-field views-field-nothing">
           <span class="field-content">
            <div class="media">
             <div class="pull-left">
              <img alt="[title_1]" src="https://philosophy.uncc.edu/sites/philosophy.uncc.edu/files/styles/news_image/public/fields/news/field_news_landscape_image/Ortega.jpg?itok=hK4TrwbX"/>
             </div>
             <div class="media-body">
              <h3>
               Mariana Ortega on Aesthetic Memory: January 24
              </h3>
              <i aria-hidden="true" class="fa fa-calendar">
              </i>
              <span class="date-display-single">
               January 15, 2019
              </span>
              <br/>
              <p>
               <a href="http://philosophy.la.psu.edu/directory/mariana-ortega" target="_blank">
                Mariana Ortega
               </a>
               , Associate Professor of Philosophy at Penn State, will give a talk on January 24 from 2:30-4:00pm at the UNC Charlotte Atkins Library (Halton Reading Room). In her talk—titled "
               <em>
                Memento Vivere
               </em>
               : Shadow Ground, Aesthetic Memory, and the Border
               <span>
                "—
               </span>
               she will discuss the production...
              </p>
              <p>
